@jokejokeboy ya u really dont get how subcontractors work... a lift upgrading projects needs X subcontractors. Each of them are middlemens who take big slices from ur 8 Million dollar contract to upgrade lifts. Now for bigger projects like HDB construction, u now need 20X subcontractors. The point being, ur net profit ends up really small compared to ur revenue. And this is before dividends and maybe stock buybacks
